---
layout: base.njk
title: Devblog
permalink: /devblog.html
---
<main>
  <div class="phero">
    <div class="eyebrow">Devblog</div>
    <h1>Working <em>notes</em></h1>
    <p class="lead">Near-daily notes on building Loupe, side projects, and whatever I'm learning across tech, the cloud, and getting better at the craft &mdash; drawn from the build log I keep as I go.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="bloglist"><div class="posts">
  {%- for post in collections.post | reverse %}
    <a class="pcard" href="{{ post.url }}">
      <div class="pmeta">{{ post.data.date | readable }}{% for t in post.data.topics %} &middot; {{ t }}{% endfor %}</div>
      <div class="ptitle">{{ post.data.title }}</div>
      <div class="psum">{{ post.data.summary }}</div>
    </a>
  {%- endfor %}
  </div></div>
</main>
